Package: bignmf
Type: Package
Title: Solving NMF via coordinate descent
Version: 0.1
Date: 2012-05-24
Author: Lanfeng Pan, Yixuan Qiu and Taiyun Wei
Maintainer: Lanfeng Pan, Yixuan Qiu and Taiyun Wei <panlanfeng@gmail.com>
Description: The bignmf package solving the nonnegative matrix factorization via alternating least square. It treats nonnegative constrained regression as a special L1 regression and solves it via coordinate descent method which is quite fast. The core code are implemented in C++ using RcppEigen. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: Rcpp(>= 0.9.10), RcppEigen(>= 0.2.0), Matrix(>= 1.0-6)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
